176
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:32,879
For us.

177
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,120
Friendship first.

178
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:35,919
Competition second.

179
00:08:36,759 --> 00:08:37,559
I'll drink up.

180
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:39,480
Don't.

181
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:42,559
Let's go.

182
00:08:53,559 --> 00:08:54,399
Are you alright?

183
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,080
Why is there

184
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,720
no smell of alcohol on him?

185
00:09:06,039 --> 00:09:07,879
He wasn't drinking wine.

186
00:09:08,399 --> 00:09:10,240
So sneaky.

187
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:12,679
Water.

188
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:14,639
Water.

189
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:16,759
Liu.

