00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,679
Water.

191
00:09:17,759 --> 00:09:18,600
I'll take her home.

192
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:20,440
But...

193
00:09:20,639 --> 00:09:21,440
I'll go.

194
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:26,960
Water.

195
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:28,720
Water.

196
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:31,440
Water.

197
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,600
Water.

198
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:36,120
What are you trying to do?

199
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,559
Why am I so dizzy?

200
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:51,584
♪When we hug, time stands still♪

201
00:09:51,872 --> 00:09:55,072
♪Because of you, my heart beats fast♪

202
00:09:55,904 --> 00:09:59,360
♪This moment, my head is in the clouds♪

203
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:02,720
♪Only you are so clear♪

204
