♪Like a faint glow in the air♪

205
00:10:07,264 --> 00:10:10,496
♪An ever-lingering sensation♪

206
00:10:11,072 --> 00:10:14,704
♪It seems we're about to get lost♪

207
00:10:15,488 --> 00:10:16,639
♪Maybe it's too late♪

208
00:10:16,639 --> 00:10:18,720
I knew it. You were

