00:10:21,824 --> 00:10:24,279
♪You stay in my heart♪

211
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:25,080
Xiao Liu.

212
00:10:26,399 --> 00:10:27,240
Xiao Liu.

213
00:10:29,568 --> 00:10:30,879
♪Etched in my memory♪

214
00:10:30,879 --> 00:10:31,679
Liu.

215
00:10:32,919 --> 00:10:33,799
